Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:08.28,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,Stepping firmly on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:11.41,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,you are awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:14.33,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,With the smile of an angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:18.34,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}take me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:29.89,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,You are not alone, even in solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:35.40,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,There is definitely a reason as to why we are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.48,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,Bathing in the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.33,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,The world is awaiting your brilliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:53.00,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,Stepping firmly on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.29,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,you are awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.29,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,With the smile of an angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:02.55,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,take me away! (you can smile!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:08.85,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,It is never too late for a ne{\fsp-13.5}w {\fsp1.5}“beginning{\fsp-25.5}”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:14.85,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}No matter what happens, keep getting back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(200,0)\blur4.5}kasanatteta mune no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:05.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(0,0)\blur4.5}yusabutte mo kikoenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:09.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(0,200)\blur4.5}koboreochita piisu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:29.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5}konna nichijou no yuutsu sae
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:35.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5}tameiki mo dezu ni mukanjou na bokura
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:50.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5}tsugihagi no kokoro wa fuantei
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:53.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5}arainagasareta shoki shoudou o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:56.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5}yobisamashite hashiridase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:00.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5}tsutanai kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:06.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur4.5}omou mama ni tsunagu yo ano hi no kodou o
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(0,400)\blur4.5}wasurenai de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(120,0)\blur4.5}The sound of overlapping hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:05.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(0,0)\blur4.5}They're vibrating, yet I can't hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:09.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(0,200)\blur4.5}The scattered pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:29.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur4.5}In spite of how depressing today is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:35.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur4.5}we show no emotion, not even a sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:37.97,EDb,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4.5}Life filled with vanity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:42.93,EDb,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur4.5}Colors have faded. Things you desire exists here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:45.72,EDb,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur4.5}Flee from this colorless world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:50.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur4.5}Our patched-up hearts are insecure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:53.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur4.5}Reawaken your primal instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:56.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur4.5}and start running.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:00.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur4.5}A clumsy choice of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:06.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur4.5}So that we can come together, as I desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(0,400)\blur4.5}don't forget that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:10.83,EDb,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4.5}Oh my lord, it's gone! What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.83,0:23:13.21,EDb,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Pieces I had have fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:15.88,EDb,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Where do you belong? Where should I aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:18.67,EDb,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur4.5}Once you've lost sight it's left to fall apart.
